    <title>Pickle存储变量到文件</title>
    <link href="https://mengfeimu.github.io/2019/03/21/tool/python-pickle/"/>
    <id>https://mengfeimu.github.io/2019/03/21/tool/python-pickle/</id>
    <published>2019-03-21T13:42:22.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-03-21T17:20:08.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>利用<code>pickle</code>包来将变量存储到一个单独的文件中，方便日后读取和处理，就不用每次都读取原始文件了。</p><h1 id="存储"><a href="#存储" class="headerlink" title="存储"></a>存储</h1><p><code>pickle.dump()</code></p><figure class="highlight python hljs"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="hljs-comment"># write hourly data to a file, read from original files costs long time</span></span><br><span class="line">tempfile = indir + <span class="hljs-string">'/tair_rh_1982_2012.dump'</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="hljs-keyword">with</span> open(tempfile, <span class="hljs-string">"wb"</span>) <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> temp:</span><br><span class="line">    pickle.dump([tair, rh], temp)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="读取"><a href="#读取" class="headerlink" title="读取"></a>读取</h1><p><code>pickle.load()</code></p><figure class="highlight python hljs"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="hljs-comment"># read hourly data from .dump files</span></span><br><span class="line">tempfile = indir + <span class="hljs-string">'/tair_rh_1982_2012.dump'</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="hljs-keyword">with</span> open(tempfile, <span class="hljs-string">'rb'</span>) <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> temp:</span><br><span class="line">    tempdata = pickle.load(temp)</span><br><span class="line">    tair, rh = tempdata[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>], tempdata[<span class="hljs-number">1</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
