    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="安装netcdf4"><a href="#安装netcdf4" class="headerlink" title="安装netcdf4"></a>安装netcdf4</h1><figure class="highlight python hljs"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">conda install -c anaconda netcdf4</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这样安装完后执行<code>import netCDF4</code>会报错：</p><figure class="highlight sql hljs"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="hljs-comment">---------------------------------------------------------------------------</span></span><br><span class="line">ImportError                               Traceback (most recent <span class="hljs-keyword">call</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">last</span>)</span><br><span class="line">&lt;ipython-<span class="hljs-keyword">input</span><span class="hljs-number">-3</span><span class="hljs-number">-9588</span>a3d4fb24&gt; <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> &lt;<span class="hljs-keyword">module</span>&gt;()</span><br><span class="line"><span class="hljs-comment">----&gt; 1 import netCDF4</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">C:\ProgramData\Miniconda3\lib\site-packages\netCDF4\__init__.py <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> &lt;<span class="hljs-keyword">module</span>&gt;()</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="hljs-number">1</span> # init <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> netCDF4. <span class="hljs-keyword">package</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="hljs-number">2</span> # Docstring comes <span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> extension <span class="hljs-keyword">module</span> _netCDF4.</span><br><span class="line"><span class="hljs-comment">----&gt; 3 from ._netCDF4 import *</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="hljs-number">4</span> # Need explicit imports <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">names</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">beginning</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">with</span> underscores</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="hljs-number">5</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> ._netCDF4 <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> __doc__, __pdoc__</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">ImportError: DLL <span class="hljs-keyword">load</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">failed</span>: The specified <span class="hljs-keyword">module</span> could <span class="hljs-keyword">not</span> be found.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>改用<code>pip install netcdf4</code>来安装，即可。</p><h1 id="nc文件读取"><a href="#nc文件读取" class="headerlink" title="nc文件读取"></a>nc文件读取</h1><figure class="highlight python hljs"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> netCDF4 <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> nc</span><br><span class="line">infile = <span class="hljs-string">'filename.nc'</span></span><br><span class="line">temp = nc.Dataset(infile)</span><br><span class="line">temp.variables[<span class="hljs-string">'TMP2m_110_HTGL'</span>][:]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
